//Home page which greets the user as they make their way to my secret database
//Extends pulls in Head, Body and Nav. Standard Bootstrap CSS/Code
extends layout
block content  

    .jumbotron.home.vertical-center
        .container
            h1.bannerh1 Your Secret Is Safe With Us
            h3.bannerh3 (We Swear It Is.)
            
    .container
        .col-lg-12.col-md-12
            h3 Your secret is safe with us! With the best security around, your secrets will be best kept here, and not that diary we saw your mother taking a glance at while she was "cleaning your room". 
        .col-lg-10.col-md-10.col-sm-8.col-xs-6.col-lg-offset-1.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-offset-2.col-xs-offset-3
            hr
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4
            i.fa.fa-lock.fa-4x
            h2 Secure
            p With this secrets database, your secrets will always be safe! So take that Stacey!
                
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4
            i.fa.fa-code.fa-4x
            h2 Node
            p We code in the Node! We remain as fast as possible, so you have short loading times.
                
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4
            i.fa.fa-unlink.fa-4x
            h2 Safe
            p Your secrets are safe here and definitely won't be on display in the bathroom stall.
        
    .jumbotron
        h4 "I use this all the time, and no one knows that I sleep with a Teddy Bear still!"
        h5 - Cole
    
    include footer